  "longBusinessSummary": "Companhia de Saneamento B\u00e1sico do Estado de S\u00e3o Paulo - SABESP provides basic and environmental sanitation services in the S\u00e3o Paulo State, Brazil. The company supplies treated water and sewage services on a wholesale basis. As of December 31, 2024, it provided water services through 9.5 million water connections; and sewage services through 8.2 million sewage connections in the 375 municipalities of the S\u00e3o Paulo State. Companhia de Saneamento B\u00e1sico do Estado de S\u00e3o Paulo - SABESP was founded in 1954 and is headquartered in S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil.",
